{
  "stem": "2581.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was at that time-- in '44 I was 16 years old-- and I said, schneider, which means tailor, because I-- I was afraid I was too young to be sent with the men.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he saw the white thread, so he sent me-- you know, he said to go to the right.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And before me-- my father was before me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And  in three days, my father had grown a beard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he became gray when he was fighting in 1920.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was a young man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was fighting for the independence of Poland against the Russians.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And at that time, he turned gray.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So he had sort of a gray beard and he looked like an old man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I don't know what came over him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I just remembered that he had in the pocket a document with this picture that he made the picture in  a spa.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he looked very young, very healthy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I put it in front of his face saying schneidermeister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is how we both went with those that were-- were supposed to-- to go to work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we never heard about our-- you know, what happened to the other people-- to our, in this case, my mother, and my brother, and all  the relatives, and the rest of the town.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How long were you in the Lodz Ghetto?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Till-- till '44.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Till August '44.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, maybe not-- about the same-- about the same time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was also about--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well in the Lask Ghetto, you know, before we were deported, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] at first, it wasn't, you know, everyone still had some connections and everyone still have some food hidden away.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were working for the peasants around in the vicinity.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
